languages.text: "Похоже, быть лучше прочих и страдать от одиночества — мой удел в любой версии реальности".
"It would seem that being better than others and suffering loneliness is my fate in every reality."
languages.original_text: "Похоже, быть лучше прочих и страдать от одиночества — мой удел в любой версии реальности".

traits.locale_text: "I guess to be better than others and suffer loneliness is my fate in every reality."
"I guess to be better than others and suffer loneliness is my fate in every reality."
"I reckon being better than others and suffering loneliness is my fate in every reality."
"I reckon being better than others and suffering loneliness is my fate in every reality."
"It would seem that being better than others and suffering loneliness is my fate in every reality."

languages.text: « Il faut croire que je suis {mf|condamné|condamnée} à être {mf|supérieur|supérieure} aux autres et à mener une existence solitaire dans toutes les réalités. »
languages.original_text: "It would seem that being better than others and suffering loneliness is my fate in every reality."

traits.locale_text: « Oui, il faut croire que je suis {mf|condamné|condamnée} à être {mf|supérieur|supérieure} aux autres et à mener une existence solitaire dans toutes les réalités. »

languages.text: «Está claro que ser superior a los demás y la soledad que eso conlleva son mi destino en todas las realidades».
languages.original_text: "It would seem that being better than others and suffering loneliness is my fate in every reality."

traits.locale_text: «Supongo que ser superior a los demás y la soledad que eso conlleva son mi destino en todas las realidades».

languages.text: “看来无论在哪个世界，我都只能忍受高处不胜寒的痛苦。这大概就是我的命运吧。”
languages.original_text: "It would seem that being better than others and suffering loneliness is my fate in every reality."

traits.locale_text: “看来无论在哪个世界，我都只能忍受高处不胜寒的痛苦。这大概就是我的命运吧。”

languages.text: 「他人より優れていること、そして孤独に苦しむことは、どのような現実においても私の宿命のようだな」
languages.original_text: "It would seem that being better than others and suffering loneliness is my fate in every reality."

traits.locale_text: 「他人より優れていること、そして孤独に苦しむことは、どのような現実においても私の宿命なのだろうな」

languages.text: "Es ist wohl einfach in jeder Realität mein Schicksal, besser zu sein als andere und daher stets einsam zu bleiben."
languages.original_text: "It would seem that being better than others and suffering loneliness is my fate in every reality."

traits.locale_text: "Es ist wohl einfach in jeder Realität mein Schicksal, besser zu sein als andere und daher stets einsam zu bleiben."
